1. Volim da pišem *rimu*. (I love to write poetry.)
2. Ona ima talenta za *rimu*. (She has talent for poetry.)
3. Ovaj stih nije u *rimi*. (This verse is not in rhyme.)
4. Da li ti se sviđa *rima* ove pesme? (Do you like the rhyme of this song?)
5. Knjiga koju sam pročitao je puna *rima*. (The book I read is full of rhymes.)
6. *Rima* nije jedini važan element poezije. (Rhyme is not the only important element of poetry.)
7. Njegov stil pisanja je prepun *rima*. (His writing style is full of rhymes.)
8. Teško je pronaći dobru *rimu* za ovaj stih. (It's difficult to find a good rhyme for this verse.)
9. Želim da naučim da pišem u *rimi*. (I want to learn how to write in rhyme.)
10. Pesma koju sam čuo juče je imala zanimljivu *rimu*. (The song I heard yesterday had an interesting rhyme.)

(Note: The word "rima" means "rhyme" in English.)